# 1. Ignore everything by default
*

# 2. But do not ignore directories themselves (so Git can look inside them)
!*/

# 3. Allow your core Python files
!Excel_to_yaml.py
!main.py
!README.md
!pyproject.toml

# 4. Allow everything inside input_files and output_yamls
!input_files/**
!output_yamls/**

# 5. Specifically block Microsoft Excel temporary/owner files inside input_files
~$*
**/~$*